Installation:
- Install cpanm, Catalyst, etc
- Run cpanm --installdeps . on the root directory
- Run plackup

Environment:
- INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_ID = your Instagram client ID
- INSTAGRAM_CLIENT_SECRET = pair of above
- FACEBOOK_APP_ID = Facebook application ID
- FACEBOOK_SECRET = pair of above
- GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID = Google Code application/client ID
- GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET = pair of above
- REDIRECT_URI = redirection URI, (defaults to http://localhost:5000)
